 <p>Don't get lost in the noise of Intuitive Machines, Inc.'s (NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LUNR\" class=\"ticker-link\">LUNR</a>) new stock offering. Although investors should have some concern over dilution, the positive developments in the company highly outweigh the negatives. For the technicals, there are indications of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151535978/image_2151535978.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742468-intuitive-machines-belongs-in-your-portfolio-wait-for-a-better-entry", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 02:31:07"}, {"id": "4742477", "title": "Veeva Systems Inc. 2025 Q3 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Veeva Systems Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q3 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106055\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742477-veeva-systems-inc-2025-q3-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 02:23:52"}, {"id": "4742238", "title": "Intel: The Board Shoots Itself In The Foot, Here's What Comes Next", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Intel Silicon Processor Chip\" data-id=\"1484082303\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484082303/image_1484082303.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750